Holiday Gift Guide for the Crypto Maxi in Your Life

Dylan Bane

Dec 9, 2024 ⋅  9 min read

Looking for the perfect gift for the crypto maxi in your life? Messari’s Crypto Gift Guide is here to help you navigate the blockchain-powered gift-giving season with ease. From cutting-edge hardware wallets and stylish merch to income-producing DePIN devices and gameboys, this guide is packed with ideas to delight everyone, from seasoned crypto veterans to curious newcomers. Whether you're spreading holiday cheer or celebrating a milestone, these handpicked options will ensure your gift resonates in a decentralized world.

DePIN

Helium Hotspot: Share Internet, Get Paid

Helium Hotspots share your internet connection with nearby devices while earning HNT tokens as a reward. Perfect for business owners or anyone with access to public spaces, these hotspots help power decentralized wireless networks while turning connectivity into a passive income opportunity.

Helium offers both indoor models ($199 with discount) and outdoor models ($399 with discount), catering to various deployment needs. Setup is straightforward and takes just a few minutes, making it accessible even for non-tech-savvy users. Once up and running, you can monitor your HNT earnings and hotspot activity directly through the Helium app.

Whether you're looking to make the most of unused bandwidth or support innovative decentralized infrastructure, Helium Hotspots are a practical and rewarding choice.

20% Off Discount Code for all Helium Hotspot Devices: HOTSPOT20

Price: $249.00–$499.00

Helium Hotspots

DIMO LTE: Drive for Tokens

The DIMO LTE is a game-changer for car owners, collecting valuable data such as battery health, fuel levels, marketplace value, and error code diagnostics—all seamlessly delivered to your smartphone. This compact, ergonomic device is incredibly easy to use: simply plug it into your car's OBD-II port, typically located under the steering wheel, and download the app to get started.

At just $169, the DIMO LTE offers an affordable entry point into the world of decentralized physical infrastructure networks (DePIN). What sets it apart is its ability to reward users with tokens for contributing vehicle data to the DIMO ecosystem—turning your car into a productive asset while providing actionable insights to improve your driving experience.

Compatible with most vehicles, the DIMO LTE is a perfect blend of utility and innovation. Plus, with reward airdrops distributed every Monday, it’s a gift that keeps on giving. Whether you're shopping for a tech enthusiast or someone looking to modernize their ride, this device offers both practicality and forward-thinking appeal.

20% Off Discount Code for the DIMO LTE: GIFTDIMO

Price: $169.00

DIMO LTE

Messari Pro Subscription: Alpha Only

Give the gift of confidence and clarity in the crypto world with a Messari Pro Subscription. Designed for investors, builders, and professionals, this platform offers trusted research, streamlined news, and powerful tools to make smarter decisions. With access to over 14,000 project profiles, 13,000 investor profiles, and customizable data visualizations, Messari Pro is the go-to resource for tracking trends and uncovering opportunities. Stay ahead with sector screeners, token unlock schedules, and performance insights updated in real time. It’s the perfect gift for anyone looking to navigate the crypto space with precision and ease.

20% Off Discount Code for Messari Pro: 100BTC

Price: $39.00/month

Messari Pro

NATIX VX360: Map the World From Your Tesla

NATIX is transforming Tesla's 360-degree camera feed into a powerful tool for gathering real-time mapping data, contributing to the advancement of next-generation autonomous vehicles. Currently in its pre-order phase, NATIX is offering a limited number of free devices, along with an exclusive discount code for early adopters. The VX360, a small and compact device, is set to ship in March at a discounted price of $245.

NATIX projects that users can recoup the cost of the device quickly through regular airdrops, rewarding contributors for their data participation. This makes the VX360 not just a cutting-edge tool for enabling autonomous vehicle innovation, but also a smart investment for Tesla owners looking to maximize the value of their car's technology.

10% Off Discount for Natix VX360: Messari10

Price: $279.99

NATIX VX360

Cudis 002: HODL Your Health Data

The perfect gift for the tech-savvy and health-conscious, the Cudis 002 is an AI-powered smart ring that not only tracks and records your health data (sleep quality, VO2, heart rate, and more) but also empowers you to monetize it. With the potential to earn over $5,000 annually from your data, the ring rewards you with points that can be redeemed for exclusive perks or future airdrops. Designed for both functionality and style, the Cudis 002 features a sleek design, comes in multiple colors, and offers a comfortable, snug fit—making it a thoughtful and innovative holiday gift.

15% Off Discount for Cudis 002: Messari

Price: $349.00

Cudis 002

Security

Lattice1: The Key to Staying SAFU

Beef up your security with the Lattice1 from Grid+, featuring a large touchscreen for readable transactions, unlimited wallet connections (through its SafeCard system), and enterprise-grade security. The Lattice1 is compatible with MetaMask, Rabby, other wallet providers, and across most major chains. While pricier than most popular wallets at $397, the Lattice1 has received rave reviews for its security, custom permissions, and intuitive interface.

Price: $397.00

Lattice1

Tangem Wallet: Not Your Keys? NGMI.

Give the gift of security and simplicity with the Tangem Wallet, a next-gen hardware wallet perfect for crypto enthusiasts. Designed like a sleek credit card, this wallet offers cold storage with advanced security, making it easy to manage digital assets safely on the go. With no batteries, no wires, and NFC-enabled functionality, users can simply tap their wallet to their smartphone for seamless access to their crypto. Ideal for beginners and experts alike, the Tangem Wallet is a thoughtful and practical gift that combines innovation, style, and peace of mind.

Price: From $54.90

Tangem Wallet

Merch

Adidas Originals x Doodles Hoodie: WAGMI in Style

Wrap up relaxation and whimsy this holiday season with the Doodles x Adidas Fleece Hoodie. Featuring the playful Doodles logo on the chest and a bold Trefoil artwork inspired by the "Touch Grass" motif on the back, this hoodie is the perfect blend of comfort and creativity. Whether you're gifting for a fan of Doodles or someone who loves unique, stylish essentials, this hoodie is a surefire way to bring warmth and cheer to the holidays.

Price: $125.00

Doodles x Adidas

9dcc Essential Structured Ball Cap: ​The Hat Stays On

Elevate their style with the 9dcc Essential Ball Cap, a perfect blend of timeless design and modern technology. Crafted with premium materials, this six-panel structured cap features minimalist branding, metal hardware accents, and a discreet adjustable strap for all-day comfort. The embroidered '9' emblem integrates NFC technology, allowing for on-chain authenticity verification and access to exclusive content and community perks with just a tap. A thoughtful gift for anyone who appreciates style, innovation, and versatility in one iconic accessory.

Price: $95.00

9dcc Essential Structured Ball Cap

Pudgy Penguin Polar Bear Plushie: Just a Chill Penguin

Looking for the perfect cuddle buddy this holiday season? Meet Polar Penny, a plush companion designed for endless snuggles. Made with soft polyester fur and stuffed with 100% cotton, this adorable toy is as cozy as it is charming. With its expressive eyes and heartwarming smile, Polar Penny is a delightful gift for all ages.

Price: $29.99

Pudgy Penguin Polar Bear Plushie

Miscellaneous

Book Bundle: A Scholar’s Guide to Escaping the Trenches

Trying to time the crypto market top? These three books dive deep into the manias of the past, how investor psychology evolved throughout cycles, and how to spot when it’s time to exit the party. Bull! focuses on bull markets of the 80s and and 90s, while The Price of Time looks at the impact ZIRP had on markets in the recent era. Mastering the Market Cycle will round it out by giving general guidelines to how market cycles typically progress and how to think through them.

Bull! - Maggie Mahar

The Price of Time - Edward Chancellor

Mastering the Market Cycle - Howard Marks

PSG1 Gameboy: Web3 Gaming, Anywhere, Anytime

Level up their gaming experience with the PSG1, the first handheld Web3 gaming device built on the Solana blockchain. Created by Play Solana, this cutting-edge console combines seamless blockchain integration with next-gen gameplay. Featuring a built-in secure hardware wallet and access to exclusive features, the PSG1 offers a revolutionary way to explore the future of gaming. Perfect for tech-savvy gamers and blockchain enthusiasts, this device is the ultimate holiday gift for those ready to embrace the next era of interactive entertainment.

Price $299.00

PSG1

Chipped: Tap, Share, and Slay

Elevate your style with Chipped, the press-on nails that are more than just a beauty upgrade. These sleek nails come with NFC chips in the thumbs, making it easy to share your socials and links with just a tap. No need to swap usernames or type out long handles—your profile is ready to go whenever you are.

Price: $64.00

Chipped

Blackbird Breakfast Club: Your Morning, Upgraded

Start your day where ideas come to life—with breakfast. The Blackbird Breakfast Club in New York gives you daily access to complimentary coffee or tea at over 20 top spots across the city, every morning until 11 a.m. But that’s just the beginning.

For $25 a month, members enjoy exclusive merch, access to members-only events, a 2,500 $FLY bonus, and quarterly runs with the Dirty Bird Run Club—perfect for channeling all that extra caffeine energy.

Price: $25.00/month

Blackbird Breakfast Club
